  <bioghist id="aspace_894ca74b2d748cdaf37984b2a1ef2714">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>Founded in 1949, the New York State Foundation cultivates, secures, and stewards financial resources to support the Cornell Cooperative Extension New York State 4-H program in developing and delivering 4-H youth development programs.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_320018ba8288fb498a1d61e907c76f0f">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Minutes of the Board of Directors and various other committee meetings, memos, financials, scholarship and trustee files.</p>  </scopecontent>
